# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusKey | Apple Developer Documentation

-  NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusKey 

Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusKey

iOS 7.0+iPadOS 7.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.9+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingStatusKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitemdownloadingstatuskey#Discussion)

The value is a string constant that indicates the download status of the item.

Possible values of the string are given in `Downloading Status Values`.
